oria also enjoys a low cost of living and is home to the Fortune    company  Caterpillar  Inc UICOMP Documents Strategic Plan Bylaws Standing Committees and Special Committees About Regional Dean Fast Facts More About the Region Visiting the Campus Contact Us About Education Research Patient Care Departments News Giving INFORMATION FOR  Prospective Students Current Students Faculty   Staff Alumni   Friends Patients RESOURCES  UIC Directory Blackboard Event Calendar Emergency Information Contact Us Apply Now Give Contact Us If you have questions  comments  or problems accessing this site  please E mail the webmaster College of Medicine Chicago Peoria Rockford Urbana 